data.description: Great location in Grove. Near Wolf Creek boat ramp and facilities.. Check this one out. Recently remodeled with new paint, flooring, HVAC and bathrooms have been remodeled with the farmhouse flair. Roof is around 7 years old. This home features 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. With 2 car garage and extra parking. Small storage building in back yard. Great garden spot. Dog pen in side yard. Awesome lake views of Wolf Creek. Big front and back yard. Privacy fence along back yard. Perfect for full time living or would be a great nightly rental unit just minutes from the boat ramp at Wolf Creek. Nearby boat slip rentals as well. Ranch style home with all one level living. Covered front porch perfect to set outside and enjoy the lake views. GV*
